{"tid":297691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去挪威真係一蚊挪威紙都唔洗唱","createTime":"2017-06-25T16:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T10:26:27.000Z","uid":25302,"like":34,"dislike":180,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e7d87fbcf0bcb34bfccc285893573460e87e89","tid":297691,"uid":25302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"連Locker 都可以用信用卡比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全用電子貨幣超爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能因為香港無人地財富咁平均<br />\n香港有好多窮人開既舖頭<br />\n例如報紙檔、cheap茶餐廳、流動小販<br />\n無錢無位裝用電子貨幣既機<br />\n所以電子貨幣流通唔倒<br />\n<br />\n相反因為北歐國家啲舖頭開得既都係有返咁上下規模<br />\n所以先可以裝電子貨幣既機"},{"pid":"78b189c6ba9a1c588acd1af1ff30ca65d8a03a02","tid":297691,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"窮人開既舖頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0f93e2b351afcc925bcab52b9695ac55c92b28","tid":297691,"uid":63864,"like":98,"dislike":3,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連Locker 都可以用信用卡比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全用電子貨幣超爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能因為香港無人地財富咁平均<br />\n香港有好多窮人開既舖頭<br />\n例如報紙檔、cheap茶餐廳、流動小販<br />\n無錢無位裝用電子貨幣既機<br />\n所以電子貨幣流通唔倒<br />\n<br />\n相反因為北歐國家啲舖頭開得既都係有返咁上下規模<br />\n所以先可以裝電子貨幣既機</blockquote><br />\n領匯未來十年將會幫你將窮人鋪頭收哂皮，你放心"},{"pid":"d50a26af197515aed0992dd4dc980d22c6ae3bed","tid":297691,"uid":38523,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"你都識講挪威啦<br />\n香港用只會比支那借頭借路電話實名制<br />\n、偷錢"},{"pid":"e2114743052a3e4ca97534605a1f05c5ea42cb5a","tid":297691,"uid":46192,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"北歐去街市買都用得信用卡"},{"pid":"b9800f63c3021114b43