dpay 咁，你個日無帶銀包想去7仔買煙又得<br />\n你唔鍾意credit card俾錢咪唔好用囉<br />\n<br />\n我唔信香港既it狗(人才)無能力開發一套又安全又可靠既支付平台<br />\n只係無人科水去做<br />\n唔係一定要用大陸做例子囉"},{"pid":"f2e4aa1a984bb09e3d225b89609b5a73b860c540","tid":297691,"uid":25302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>北歐去街市買都用得信用卡</blockquote><br />\n好撚爽咁</blockquote><br />\n去完挪威玩左咁多日<br />\n到走都未見過挪威紙係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用歐羅會唔會俾人屌？</blockquote><br />\n純信用卡<br />\n無比過歐羅唔知"},{"pid":"95c8040ea5c3f96a9fa77b1840015b0dfb2207ae","tid":297691,"uid":25302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Oslo有咩好玩 玩到幾多日？<br />\n有無去Bergen</blockquote><br />\n去行山多<br />\nkjeragbolten 同惡魔之舌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOslo 就都係市中心個公園、博物館<br />\n都係去感受啲嘢有幾貴同有幾少人"},{"pid":"50be93ca0eddf92dba4dd5f3bda2cb71fd979f5c","tid":297691,"uid":25302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔駛起連登再講架電子貨幣啦<br />\n其實3點<br />\n1 多d選擇，除左老八信用卡現金，市民值得多一兩種支付平台去揀<br />\n2 自由市場，唔好唔受歡迎好自然會被淘汰<br />\n3 屌你老母出左你驚咪唔好撚用，好似用槍逼你咁<br />\n<br />\n但你同佢地講「多d選擇」「市場淘汰」<br />\n佢地就會同返你講監察<br />\n<br />\n佢地好似覺得一推佢地一定要用咁<br />\n好似政府用槍迫全香港人都要用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似applepay andriodpay 咁，你個日無帶銀包想去7仔買煙又得<br />\n你唔鍾意credit card俾錢咪唔好用囉<br />\n<br />\n我唔信香港既it狗(人才)無能力開發一套又安全又可靠既支付平台<br />\n只係無人科水去做<br />\n唔係一定要用大陸做例子囉</blockquote><br />\n啱<br />\n不過香港蠢人太多<br />\n一啲柒既系統都實有好多人用"},{"pid":"4c277e561734cb3baf72ff4ba365cbfb101dfc4b","tid":297691,"uid":8511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n啱<br />\n不過香港蠢人太多<br />\n一啲柒既系統都實有好多人用</blockquote><br />\n蠢人用咪由得蠢人被盜個人資料被監控<br />\n你覺得柒咪唔好用<br />\n你覺得佢會監察你用你資料搵錢咪唔好用<br />\n好簡單"},{"pid":"b20b6b1bd6393c2510ee5196e80118f367c0f6be","tid":297691,"uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T18:03:59.000Z","msg":"其實北歐每個國家都先進過香港同好多地方"},{"pid":"3c9629d8984bcbdc8215c17195ed86f0fb8aea73","tid":297691,"uid":43314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Oslo有咩好玩 玩到幾多日？<br />\n有無去Bergen</blockquote><br />\nBergen 必去，反而 oslo 去唔去都得"},{"pid":"85fa129fc5d33dfbe84781b030a9f07d1a42ce6e","tid":297691,"uid":43314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>北歐去街市買都用得信用卡</blockquote><br />\n好撚爽咁</blockquote><br />\n去完挪威玩左咁多日<br />\n到走都未見過挪威紙係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用歐羅會唔會俾人屌？</blockquote><br />\n純信用卡<br />\n無比過歐羅唔知</blockquote><br />\n可以，但個 rate 貴 d"},{"pid":"c19a8b1f1cdf330053448b7869846ea21e3f4239","tid":297691,"uid":33961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Oslo有咩好玩 玩到幾多日？<br />\n有無去Bergen</blockquote><br />\nBergen 必去，反而 oslo 去唔去都得</blockquote><br />\n無錯, bergen 淨係行上山去觀境台睇日落+夜境已經正到喊<br />\n<br />\n反而 oslo 得 d 博物館, city hall 睇, 怕悶既可以唔去"},{"pid":"ab6bf75432eb45dcfa02194d7329cd0569f9ea61","tid":297691,"uid":66126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"應該要出debit card"},{"pid":"9f0f5b16def7a57959abbe7f2f607f78463d3908","tid":297691,"uid":66126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實北歐每個國家都先進過香港同好多地方</blockquote><br />\n香港落後左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8157ab9ffe1325f8243caee7b29cb55ea1c0dae","tid":297691,"uid":33961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>北歐去街市買都用得信用卡</blockquote><br />\n好撚爽咁</blockquote><br />\n去完挪威玩左咁多日<br />\n到走都未見過挪威紙係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用歐羅會唔會俾人屌？</blockquote><br />\n純信用卡<br />\n無比過歐羅唔知</blockquote><br />\n之前去係香港唱定600 歐帶去用, 返返香港仲有550 歐到淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左搭巴士要比現金之外(前提唔買 pass), 一張 visa 已經通行"},{"pid":"e36ce5fad7e5b1939674126199d13da1751129ad","tid":297691,"uid":30272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"香港要實行都要班細鋪肯啦<br />\n稅務問題"},{"pid":"3b7aed71ad31a1fa29b79110638af9f6863a6f8a","tid":297691,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連Locker 都可以用信用卡比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全用電子貨幣超爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能因為香港無人地財富咁平均<br />\n香港有好多窮人開既舖頭<br />\n例如報紙檔、cheap茶餐廳、流動小販<br />\n無錢無位裝用電子貨幣既機<br />\n所以電子貨幣流通唔倒<br />\n<br />\n相反因為北歐國家啲舖頭開得既都係有返咁上下規模<br />\n所以先可以裝電子貨幣既機</blockquote><br />\n領匯未來十年將會幫你將窮人鋪頭收哂皮，你放心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經收得8899啦，比窮人幫靚的舖頭所餘無幾啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd93e01392f70c48c728be2046f9b09b6fcbcb3","tid":297691,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港要實行都要班細鋪肯啦<br />\n稅務問題</blockquote><br />\n正解，大把人避稅呃津"},{"pid":"8fa59fe4f1db8d59b7bb49fe78b1adb4f28e436c","tid":297691,"uid":61517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得主要係政府推唔推廣既問題<br />\n當然呢樣野要由大商戶做起 當電子貨幣成為主流 大家習慣左呢種模式 自然每間鋪頭都會裝電子支付系統<br />\n而事實上我都唔覺得呢套系統會有幾貴 但好處真係多到講唔晒 方便唔洗每日數錢 又唔洗驚找錯錢<br />\n個人黎講一禁個制就見到每日每個月洗左幾多錢 用左黎做咩etc 絕對係百利而無一害 唯一諗到就係有機會比人hack</blockquote><br />\n利申 人在丹麥<br />\n人地連食飯夾錢都係用app 我呢啲冇當地bank acc既就成個傻仔咁比cash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話用就等於發達,而係有一樣科技既出現為大家帶來方便,點解唔嘗試推廣佢? 點解成班扯晒去&quot;唔用唔代表唔發達&quot;, &quot;香港點都發達過大陸&quot;呢啲九唔搭八既觀點?<br />\n有咁多發達國家全面普及左呢樣野,叫香港人試下用係咪真係咁難</blockquote><br />\n而家啲窮人舖頭(報紙檔、街坊茶餐廳、街市)<br />\n都係啲阿叔阿婆開<br />\n唔會試新野<br />\n但偏偏就最多人幫襯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照你咁講問題好易解決，殺曬d窮人咪得囉"},{"pid":"e4097d648886704316b026c0508763bdc2bea1d9","tid":297691,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:44:08.000Z","msg":"其實隔離的土匪黨，近日不斷想在香港推行它們的可無限印發的電子貨幣，到底所謂何事！<br />\n想港幣消失，及濫發多陪虛擬貨幣，然後把香港人的資產收歸土匪黨其下？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981e21e4f36f06c33687edad167eedcc434bf2b9","tid":297691,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:46:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac865f1bdc66173d838e88adf1b14f170688b45c","tid":297691,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:47:45.000Z","msg":"講到無窮人得連鎖就會有無線比錢<br />\n大家樂大快活吉野家同d大型連鎖酒樓都無啦<br />\n隨口都數到d去得最多既飲食鋪頭都無"},{"pid":"72390b0fff17e52983e263b036bfa45041bffa85","tid":297691,"uid":27388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:48:44.000Z","msg":"因為香港用現金可以整到條數剛剛好，唔洗交稅"},{"pid":"52acc99b5b8d75e97ac4f2ee502bcc73a9f29e45","tid":297691,"uid":36780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:50:40.000Z","msg":"咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b675